"a.容易做的；肤浅的 【英】 adj.容易做的(easy) ；肤浅的(superficial) 【记】 fac(做)+ile(能…的) →能做的→容易的 【例】 I completed the facile task quickly. adj. 容易做的; 肤浅的 = superficial 【记】fac(做), ile(能...的)－能做的－容易的 【反】arduous(adj 费劲的); profound(adj 深刻的; 意义深远的) 【记】类似superficial ；facilitate 是使容易，facile 是容易 facile (adj.)  late 15c., from Middle French facile ""easy,"" from Latin facilis ""easy to do"" and, of persons, ""pliant, courteous,"" from facere ""to do"" (see factitious)."
